<title>USA: Nutrition For Life names Barry Loder COO.</title>
<headline>Nutrition For Life names Barry Loder COO.</headline>
<dateline>HOUSTON 1997-04-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Nutrition For Life International said Monday Barry Loder was appointed chief operating officer.</p>
<p>The company said Loder is also the company's vice president and chief financial officer.</p>
<p>The company said David Bertrand, the company's president and Chief Executive Officer, was also handling the COO responsibilties before Loder was appointed to the job.</p>
<p>Nutrition For Life makes and sells nutritional supplements and other consumer products.</p>
